Probabilistic Methods, Rule Learning. 

Probabilistic Methods: The paper evaluates the discretization methods with respect to Naive-Bayesian classifiers, which are probabilistic models.

Rule Learning: The paper presents a discretization method based on the C4.5 decision tree algorithm, which is a rule learning algorithm. The paper also compares this method to an existing entropy-based discretization algorithm and a recently proposed error-based technique.
